{"tid":1674794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有好多小店等大家去懲罰架 牛頭角茶理史今日得2000蚊生意咋","createTime":"2019-10-25T12:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T07:23:06.000Z","uid":162804,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c491ecb4f8b146f764197435f59a26f118a0ec","tid":1674794,"uid":162804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:06:09.000Z","msg":"今日收工諗住去幫襯下 係隔離聽到店員話今日得2000蚊收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得呢間當時都有參加罷工，絕對非偽黃店<br />\n其實都知大家都好想去懲罰黃店，但除左出名果幾間仲有好多小店需要你地去懲罰架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其迫死一間做死staff不如分散投資，咁先係winwin呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKdhrJz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKdhrJz.png&h=bee9d77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘友牛頭角友收工經過不如去支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c805af9cc628b4e4c98769df819b34a070d490","tid":1674794,"uid":275891,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"你地班撚樣 係咪三分鐘熱度阿<br />\n每晚十點無人應！<br />\n成日話抖抖抖 每晚十點都要抖？"},{"pid":"a0b7daae1a7d3b04143e0b2b65c8ac1523ddd047","tid":1674794,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"662ab89145a3092b3f24c44542b7628558289a39","tid":1674794,"uid":324892,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b2b5714761485beac929416e7890d379a58ddd6","tid":1674794,"uid":322301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:16:20.000Z","msg":"有無證據睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337ff4e35b877026d948f6b01c57db91bfdbbdab","tid":1674794,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-2